{"tid":2288242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葵廣仆街死老變態賤格淫蟲出沒注意！！","createTime":"2020-11-16T10:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T11:47:32.000Z","uid":106521,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d72403799040c19b3fcfcbb1ef506f9c4dc9bd68","tid":2288242,"uid":106521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Nnqs3g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Nnqs3g.png&h=d9e42254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱係葵廣行行下企左一陣覆msg <br />\n明明成條路無咩人見條死淫蟲鬼鬼祟崇行到勁近<br />\n已經覺得怪怪 退開一步比佢過<br />\n條死pk 仲夠膽死夾硬用個手踭撞埋黎我個胸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一野推撚開佢問佢做乜撚野 然後佢跑走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個下反應唔切無追上去影正面<br />\n仆街真係好嘔心好賤格<br />\n大家係街一定要小心<br />\n小心d 死變態唔好比機會佢博自己或者女朋友朦<br />\n依加都嬲撚到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c571ba805139149f7d34583069a91b2a23641717","tid":2288242,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"287a28acad2ef5575f70af59d71d54c5778c7663","tid":2288242,"uid":40836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d3f3dd9f6ef6d118dd44f098e9f5769ae424802d","tid":2288242,"uid":282708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"大叫非禮"},{"pid":"b009e7d7546eac43331eccf468affd98418782eb","tid":2288242,"uid":301139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0db1d59b0cb5b22e479a7ddfcffa27bf87901665","tid":2288242,"uid":318414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認住呢d仆街鹹濕廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錢去叫雞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=